            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Caecilius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Pap</abbr><ex>iria</ex></expan> Optatus <lb n="3"/>|(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fel</abbr><ex>icis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>et |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apollin</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>missus honesta <lb n="6"/>missione ab <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoribus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">arco</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Antonino et <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Vero <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> atlectus <note>sic</note> a <expan><abbr>Barc</abbr><ex>inonensibus</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>inter immunes <expan><abbr>consecut</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>in honores aedilicios <lb n="11"/>IIvir III <expan><abbr>flam</abbr><ex>en</ex></expan> Romae <lb n="12"/>divorum et Augustorum <lb n="13"/>qui <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ei</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Barc</abbr><ex>inonensium</ex></expan> ita <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> do lego <lb n="14"/>darique volo |(denariorum) |(septem milia) D ex <lb n="15"/>quorum usuris semissibus <lb n="16"/>edi volo quodannis <expan><abbr>spectac</abbr><ex>ulum</ex></expan> <lb n="17"/>pugilum die IIII Iduum <expan><abbr>Iuni</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> <lb n="18"/>usque at |(denarios) CCL et eadem die <lb n="19"/>ex |(denariis) CC oleum in thermis <expan><abbr>public</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="20"/>populo praeberi et haec ita praes<lb break="no" n="21"/>tari ea condicione volo ut <lb n="22"/>liberti mei item libertorum meorum <lb n="23"/>libertarumque liberti quos <lb n="24"/>honor <lb n="25"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Seviratus contige<lb break="no" n="2"/>rit ab omnibus mu<lb break="no" n="3"/>neribus seviratus ex<lb break="no" n="4"/>cusati sint quot si quis <lb n="5"/>eorum at munera <lb n="6"/>vocitus fuerit <lb n="7"/>tum ea |(denariorum) |(septem milia) D at <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>rem <expan><abbr>pub</abbr><ex>licam</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tarrac</abbr><ex>onensium</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>transferri iubeo <lb n="10"/>sub eadem forma <lb n="11"/>spectaculorum quot <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptum</ex></expan> est edendorum <lb n="13"/>Tarracone
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Die Inschrift verteilt sich auf zwei benachbarte Seiten. Die Buchstabenhöhe bezieht sich auf Text 1 und 2; Text 3: 1.4-2.4. Text 2 befindet sich unter Text 1 auf derselben Seite. Text 1: Z. 6: auch Ergänzung M(arcis) möglich.</p>
            </div>
